a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Adrian Pop\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6396:\"<p><img class=\"alignright\" title=\"WordCamp București 2016\"  src=\"//i1.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/3/8/e/global_418550062.jpeg\" alt=\"WordCamp București 2016\" /><br />\nDragi prieteni,</p>\n<p>Ultima noastră întâlnire WordPress pe 2016 vine într-o zi specială. Haideți să sărbătorim  cea de-a 24 ediție împreună într-un alt format, dedicat prieteniei.</p>\n<p>Așadar vă așteptăm la aceeași locație, Impact Hub pe Strada Halelor 5 din București, <strong>marți, 6 decembrie</strong>, de la <strong>18:45</strong> la <strong>21:00</strong>.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-1565\"></span></p>\n<p>Împreună cu invitatul nostru special<b> Orlando Petriceanu </b>vom experimenta și învăța noi tehnici de a rămâne autentic în situații provocatoare. Orlando este <em>trainer</em>, <em>entertainer</em> și <em>communication and public speaking coach</em>. Aveți <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZX0KerYYGtSxmNWJTtDQcA\" target=\"_blank\">aici mai multe</a> despre munca lui.</p>\n<p>Fără alte spoilere, totuși.</p>\n<p>A G E N D A</p>\n<table class=\"widefat\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid #aaa;border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"alt\">\n<td>18:45</td>\n<td>Sosiri</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>19:00</td>\n<td>Întâmpinare cu pizza</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"alt\">\n<td>19:30</td>\n<td>Workshop despre construirea comunității cu Orlando Petriceanu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>21:00</td>\n<td>Sfârșitul întâlnirii &#8230;ce va continua la un pahar de vorbă în Centrul Vechi.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em>Aceste întâlniri sunt cu intrare liberă, oricine este binevenit.<br />\nAdu un prieten, răspândește poezia!</em></p>\n<style type=\"text/css\">#meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix:after { visibility: hidden; display: block; font-size: 0; content: \" \"; clear: both; height: 0; }* html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix, *:first-child+html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix { zoom: 1; }#meetup_oembed { background:#eee;border:1px solid #ccc;padding:10px;-moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;margin:0; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; }#meetup_oembed h3 { font-weight:normal; margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:26px; font-family:Georgia,Palatino,serif; font-size:24px }#meetup_oembed p { margin: 0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:16px; }#meetup_oembed img { border:none; margin:0; padding:0; }#meetup_oembed a, #meetup_oembed a:visited, #meetup_oembed a:link { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: none; cursor: hand; cursor: pointer; }#meetup_oembed a:hover { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: underline; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button { font-size:14px; -moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;border:2px solid #A7241D;color:white!important;text-decoration:none;background-color: #CA3E47; background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ca3e47, #a8252e); background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left bottom, left top, color-stop(0, #a8252e), color-stop(1, #ca3e47));disvplay:inline-block;padding:5px 10px; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button:hover { color: #fff!important; text-decoration: none; }#meetup_oembed .photo { width:50px; height:50px; overflow:hidden;background:#ccc;float:left;margin:0 5px 0 0;text-align:center;padding:1px; }#meetup_oembed .photo img { height:50px }#meetup_oembed .number { font-size:18px; }#meetup_oembed .thing { text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; }</style>\n<div id=\"meetup_oembed\" style=\"height:302px\">\n<div style=\"max-height:262px;overflow:hidden\">\n<h3>December WordPress Meetup</h3>\n<p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px\">Tuesday, Dec 6, 2016,  7:00 PM</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Impact Hub Bucharest</span><br /><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Strada Halelor 5 Bucharest, RO</span></p>\n<p>          <span style=\"color:#4F8A10;font-size:16px;\">38 WordPressers Attending</span>           </p>\n<div style=\"margin:5px 0 10px\" class=\"mu_clearfix\">\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/d/0/6/thumb_260055622.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/3/1/2/thumb_255385362.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/f/9/8/thumb_260656280.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/6/a/1/thumb_262342177.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/b/0/4/thumb_257719204.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/a/9/f/thumb_262251871.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/b/1/4/thumb_252875604.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/c/2/4/thumb_258015396.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/4/8/5/thumb_262229829.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/4/6/4/thumb_254181604.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/6/d/a/thumb_262334042.jpeg\" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style=\"line-height:16px\">Dear friends,Our last WordPress meetup for 2016 is coming up on a special day. Let’s celebrate the 24th edition together in a different kind of session dedicated to friendship.Together with our special guest Orlando Petriceanu we will experiment and learn new techniques for staying authentic in challenging situations. Orlando is a trainer, entert&#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Bucharest-WordPress-Meetup/events/235816975/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"mu_button\"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sperăm că acest an a fost unul bun pentru tine. Îți suntem recunoscători că ne-am cunoscut și pentru că împreună construim comunitatea WordPress din România.</p>\n<p>Să ne vedem cu bine!<br />\n<img class=\"size-medium aligncenter\" src=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/7/4/d/600_456342829.jpeg\" width=\"403\" height=\"403\" /></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://ro.wordpress.org/2016/12/05/wordpress-meetup-intalnirea-din-decembrie/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"WordPress Meetup – Întalnirea din noiembrie\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://ro.wordpress.org/2016/11/10/wordpress-meetup-intalnirea-din-noiembrie/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b: